    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā vaṅgīso sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time Venerable Vaṅgīsa was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā vaṅgīso aciraarahattappatto hutvā vimuttisukhaṃ paṭisaṃvedī tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
          "en": "Now at that time Vaṅgīsa had recently attained perfection. While experiencing the bliss of freedom, on that occasion he recited these verses: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:2.1",
          "pli": "“Kāveyyamattā vicarimha pubbe, ",
          "en": "“We used to wander, drunk on poetry, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:2.2",
          "pli": "Gāmā gāmaṃ purā puraṃ; ",
          "en": "village to village, town to town. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:2.3",
          "pli": "Athaddasāma sambuddhaṃ, ",
          "en": "Then we saw the Buddha, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:2.4",
          "pli": "Saddhā no upapajjatha. ",
          "en": "and faith arose in us. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:3.1",
          "pli": "So me dhammamadesesi, ",
          "en": "He taught me Dhamma: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:3.2",
          "pli": "khandhāyatanadhātuyo; ",
          "en": "the aggregates, sense fields, and elements. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:3.3",
          "pli": "Tassāhaṃ dhammaṃ sutvāna, ",
          "en": "When I heard his teaching "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:3.4",
          "pli": "pabbajiṃ anagāriyaṃ. ",
          "en": "I went forth to homelessness. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:4.1",
          "pli": "Bahunnaṃ vata atthāya, ",
          "en": "It was truly for the benefit of many "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:4.2",
          "pli": "bodhiṃ ajjhagamā muni; ",
          "en": "that the sage achieved awakening—"
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:4.3",
          "pli": "Bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnañca, ",
          "en": "for the monks and for the nuns "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:4.4",
          "pli": "ye niyāmagataddasā. ",
          "en": "who see that they’ve reached certainty. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:5.1",
          "pli": "Svāgataṃ vata me āsi, ",
          "en": "It was so welcome for me "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:5.2",
          "pli": "mama buddhassa santike; ",
          "en": "to be in the presence of the Buddha. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:5.3",
          "pli": "Tisso vijjā anuppattā, ",
          "en": "I’ve attained the three knowledges, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:5.4",
          "pli": "kataṃ buddhassa sāsanaṃ. ",
          "en": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:6.1",
          "pli": "Pubbenivāsaṃ jānāmi, ",
          "en": "I know my past lives, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:6.2",
          "pli": "Dibbacakkhuṃ visodhitaṃ; ",
          "en": "my clairvoyance is purified, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:6.3",
          "pli": "Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, ",
          "en": "I am master of three knowledges, attained in psychic power, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:6.4",
          "pli": "Cetopariyāyakovido”ti. ",
          "en": "cxpert in comprehending the minds of others.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.1",
          "pli": "Nikkhantaṃ arati ceva, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.2",
          "pli": "pesalā atimaññanā; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.3",
          "pli": "Ānandena subhāsitā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.4",
          "pli": "sāriputtapavāraṇā; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.5",
          "pli": "Parosahassaṃ koṇḍañño, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.6",
          "pli": "moggallānena gaggarā; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.7",
          "pli": "Vaṅgīsena dvādasāti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn8.12:7.8",
          "pli": "Vaṅgīsasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. ",
          "en": "The Linked Discourses with Vaṅgīsa are complete."
        }
      ],
